 -- Christian Schoenebeck <cuse@users.sourceforge.net>  Sun, 01 Jun 2014 00:39:04 +0200

libgig (3.3.0-4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added Linux/POSIX ported version of libakai. Note that libakai is released
    under LGPL terms while libgig is released under GPL terms. To handle this
    license difference appropriately the AKAI support part is built as separate
    DLL (.so file). Due to its low expected demand however, no separate package
    is created for the AKAI part for now though.
  * Updated package descriptions.

 -- Christian Schoenebeck <cuse@users.sourceforge.net>  Thu, 22 May 2014 00:58:12 +0200

